<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="586" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,387,594]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,503,495,521]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Diagnosis (partial, male).</emphasis>
Males are morphologically similar to those of 
<taxonomicName authority="Zonstein, 2007" authorityName="Zonstein" authorityYear="2007" box="[1042,1354,495,522]" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bentzieni">
<emphasis box="[1042,1059,496,521]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1075,1176,495,521]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">bentzieni</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Zonstein, S. L." box="[1185,1354,495,521]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" pagination="15 - 17" refId="ref4063" refString="Zonstein, S. L. (2007) A new species of the mygalomorph spider genus Brachythele Ausserer, 1871 (Aranei: Nemesiidae) from Greece. Arthropoda Selecta, 16, 15 - 17." type="journal article" year="2007">Zonstein, 2007</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein, 2022" authorityName="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein" authorityYear="2022" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodopensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">B. rhodopensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[294,356,531,557]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[294,356,531,557]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
by having an embolic keel, but can be distinguished by the thin, curved embolic portion (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 7–12" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1916,1940]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,617,1893]" captionTargetId="figure-145@3.[151,1436,617,1893]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 7–12. Brachythele rhodopensis sp. n., holotype male, palp (7–9) and Brachythele langourovi, paratype, male, palp (10–12). 7, 10 prolateral; 8, 11 ventral; 9, 12 retrolateral. Scale 0.5 mm." pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Figs 10, 12</figureCitation>
) vs. more massive in 
<taxonomicName authority="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein, 2022" authorityName="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein" authorityYear="2022" box="[425,592,567,593]" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodopensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[425,592,567,593]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">B. rhodopensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[599,663,567,593]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[599,663,567,593]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[677,778,567,593]" captionStart="FIGURES 7–12" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1916,1940]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,617,1893]" captionTargetId="figure-145@3.[151,1436,617,1893]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 7–12. Brachythele rhodopensis sp. n., holotype male, palp (7–9) and Brachythele langourovi, paratype, male, palp (10–12). 7, 10 prolateral; 8, 11 ventral; 9, 12 retrolateral. Scale 0.5 mm." pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Figs 7–9</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[790,861,567,594]" captionStart="FIGURES 13–15" captionStartId="4.[151,264,959,983]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,273,935]" captionTargetId="figure-52@4.[151,1436,272,935]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 13–15. Brachythele rhodopensis sp. n., holotype male, palp. 13 prolateral; 14 ventral; 15 retrolateral. T—tegulum; E—embolus; K—embolic keel. Scale 0.5 mm." pageId="3" pageNumber="586">13–15</figureCitation>
) and straighter in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zonstein" authorityYear="2007" box="[1065,1197,567,594]" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bentzieni">
<emphasis box="[1065,1082,568,593]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1096,1197,567,593]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">bentzieni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[1212,1344,567,593]" captionStart="FIGURES 26–27" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1657,1681]" captionTargetBox="[151,1427,781,1634]" captionTargetId="figure-286@7.[151,1436,777,1634]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 26–27. Brachythele bentzieni, male palp. 26 ventral; 27 retrolateral. Scale 0.5 mm." pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Figs 26–27</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption pageId="3" pageNumber="586" startId="3.[151,264,1916,1940]" targetBox="[151,1436,617,1893]" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1916,1977]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,328,1916,1941]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">FIGURES 7–12.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein, 2022" authorityName="Dimitrov &amp; Zonstein" authorityYear="2022" box="[334,586,1917,1941]" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodopensis" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[334,586,1917,1941]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Brachythele rhodopensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[594,651,1917,1941]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[594,651,1917,1941]" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, holotype male, palp (7–9) and 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Naumova, Hristovski &amp; Hristov" authorityYear="2016" box="[977,1217,1917,1941]" class="Arachnida" family="Nemesiidae" genus="Brachythele" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="586" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="langourovi">
<emphasis box="[977,1217,1917,1941]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">Brachythele langourovi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, paratype, male, palp 
<emphasis box="[151,232,1953,1977]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="586">(10–12)</emphasis>
. 7, 10 prolateral; 8, 11 ventral; 9, 12 retrolateral. Scale 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
